title: Bill being passed to ban Tiktok in US
text:
Tiktok is currently planned to be banned in the Unites States.
My experience was good, although many encounters were no bueno. This would include Live and the video comment features. 

Many love to do inappropriate and irrelevant things on Live, such as sexual content including twerking, racist content, polls about voting for a specific president, country wars and much more. 

Comments get annoying, majority caused by younger audiences. Insults can get thousands of likes on vides and comments.

Tiktok is a good app, although it seems to be the communities fault. Tiktok has a report feature which works.

title: Wonderful app
text: This app allows many to share ideas and concepts that come from people with different backgrounds and opinions. I think it has become a valuable source of free speech and education for many. Sure there are some things that may be offensive. There are some who wish to spread negativity. But the good always outweighs the bad. The masses can choose what they want to allow into their conscious minds. If there are overt hate agendas being presented, then they should be illuminated. But open minded concepts should be free for all to explore.
